HEADWORD: Snotty
<hw>Snot"ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Foul with snot; hence,
mean; dirty.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Snot"ti*ly</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
